{"tid":1611732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[1月31截止提名]2百萬+1香港市民有資格提名諾貝爾和平獎嗎？","createTime":"2019-10-02T04:43:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T05:10:28.000Z","uid":127381,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4a76cf0ba87a1f422dcff1babbe17d8ff580fc22","tid":1611732,"uid":127381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:43:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.nobelprize.org/nomination/peace/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nobelprize.org%2Fnomination%2Fpeace%2F&d=9ZkxwAQN0Q6nkyzE8ymhdAKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=a1335ae1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nobelprize.org/nomination/peace/</a><br />\n<br />\n原文在上。大致上係每年9月至1月31日接受提名<br />\n提名者必須為（原文有更多但有d唔識譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）：<br />\n- 政府機構<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n- 海牙國際法庭成員<br />\n- 歷史/社會科學/法律/哲學/宗教等大學教授<br />\n- 前諾貝爾和平獎得主/機構成員<br />\n<br />\n雖然我都明白做呢d野未必幫到香港現況<br />\n但相信一齊站上國際舞台係香港人既唯一出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50ad380e1e0d3f0dda4883e65b479ce9b6e4fc6b","tid":1611732,"uid":127381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:44:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nP牌求推"},{"pid":"e116545456aea422dd93e3f560465fb391bd4108","tid":1611732,"uid":325698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a76cf0ba87a1f422dcff1babbe17d8ff580fc22","tid":1611732,"uid":127381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:43:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.nobelprize.org/nomination/peace/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nobelprize.org%2Fnomination%2Fpeace%2F&d=9ZkxwAQN0Q6nkyzE8ymhdAKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=a1335ae1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nob